  "title": "Senior Preschool English Educator",
  "description": "<p><u>Key Responsibilities</u></p><ul><li><strong>Children’s Learning & Development</strong><br />Implement engaging lesson plans, creative activities, and experiential learning experiences that meet the diverse needs of children and foster their holistic development.</li><li><strong>Custodial Care</strong><br />Ensure the safety, well-being, and personal hygiene of children while helping them feel secure and supported in their environment.</li><li><strong>Class Management</strong><br />Create a positive and structured learning environment through effective classroom management and the use of positive discipline strategies.</li><li><strong>Evaluation & Reporting</strong><br />Observe, assess, and document children’s progress, addressing any developmental concerns in collaboration with parents and supervisors.</li><li><strong>Collaboration & Mentoring</strong><br />Build strong relationships with families, communicate children’s progress effectively, and mentor new teachers and interns by sharing best practices.</li></ul>",
