    "description": "<p><strong>KINDERLAND INTERNATIONAL EDUCATION PTE LTD </strong>is a member of Crestar Education Group, a leading provider of quality infant care and bilingual preschool education for children 2 months to 6 years of age.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>KINDERLAND INTERNATIONAL's </strong>success in nurturing confident children has led to an extensive regional preschool network of over 60 centres located in Singapore, China, Malaysia, Indonesia, Vietnam, Cambodia and Bangladesh.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If you have the passion to make a difference in the lives of the little ones, we have the passion to make a difference in your journey with us!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>At <strong>KINDERLAND INTERNATIONAL</strong>, we track your career progression, provide the necessary training for career advancements and even provide opportunities overseas with our regional preschools.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>And, if you are looking at careers outside of preschool, your journey with us may land you in positions such as Cluster Principals, Curriculum Specialists and many more!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>So, sign up with <strong>KINDERLAND INTERNATIONAL</strong> and grow your career with us!</p>",
